  "title": "Sunkissed Mirage",
  "secondName": "Sunkissed Mirage",
  "description": "Elmina didn't grow up with tropical heat, but she thinks it suits her. Humidity works wonders for her complexion, and the sun brings out the natural highlights in her hair. She doesn't have to worry about burns much either, though Callen still lectures her until she puts on proper protection.\n\nStill, when the sun grows too bright even for her, she enjoys a cool retreat into the forest. Walking through the shade at the hottest time of day is a rare pleasure for one used to shivering in the cold.\n\nAnd stumbling upon an unexpected waterfall? That's the kind of memory that begs to be shared with another.",
